    class Patches(L.Layer):
    def __init__(self, patch_size):
        super(Patches, self).__init__()
        self.patch_size = patch_size

    def call(self, images):
        batch_size = tf.shape(images)[0]
        patches = tf.image.extract_patches(
            images = images,
            sizes = [1, self.patch_size, self.patch_size, 1],
            strides = [1, self.patch_size, self.patch_size, 1],
            rates = [1, 1, 1, 1],
            padding = 'VALID',
        )
        patch_dims = patches.shape[-1]
        patches = tf.reshape(patches, [batch_size, -1, patch_dims])
        return patches
    class Patches(L.Layer): def __init__(self, patch_size): super(Patches, self).__init__() self.patch_size = patch_size def call(self, images): batch_size = tf.shape(images)[0] patches = tf.image.extract_patches( images = images, sizes = [1, self.patch_size, self.patch_size, 1], strides = [1, self.patch_size, self.patch_size, 1], rates = [1, 1, 1, 1], padding = 'VALID', ) patch_dims = patches.shape[-1] patches = tf.reshape(patches, [batch_size, -1, patch_dims]) return patches
